<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:12:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国人权事务高级专员称中国在新疆和西藏实施侵犯人权行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/un-rights-chief-says-china-committing-violations-xinjiang-tibet-2024-03-04/</link><description>联合国人权事务高级专员沃尔克·特克周一呼吁中国落实建议，修改侵犯基本权利的法律，包括在新疆和西藏地区。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/un-rights-chief-says-china-committing-violations-xinjiang-tibet-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国长电科技将收购西部数据闪存工厂股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/jcet-buy-80-stake-sandisk-chinas-unit-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国芯片组装和测试公司长电科技集团周一表示，计划以约 6.24 亿美元现金收购西部数据公司旗下上海一家闪存工厂 80% 的股权。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/jcet-buy-80-stake-sandisk-chinas-unit-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>独家：草案显示，欧盟希望化石燃料行业帮助支付应对气候变化的费用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/eu-wants-fossil-fuel-sector-help-pay-combat-climate-change-draft-shows-2024-03-04/</link><description>一份文件草案显示，随着各国准备今年就全球金融目标进行谈判，欧盟将呼吁化石燃料行业根据联合国的目标，帮助支付较贫穷国家应对气候变化的费用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/eu-wants-fossil-fuel-sector-help-pay-combat-climate-change-draft-shows-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构会议开始之际，西方避免与伊朗发生严重对抗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/west-avoids-seriously-confronting-iran-iaea-meet-begins-2024-03-04/</link><description>外交官们表示，联合国核监督机构主要决策机构的季度会议于周一开始，西方大国再次选择不认真对抗伊朗，因为伊朗未能在一系列问题上与该机构合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/west-avoids-seriously-confronting-iran-iaea-meet-begins-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔在望，股市保持纪录，日经指数突破 40,000 点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国电池巨头宁德时代拟在香港设立研发中心以支持技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国电池巨头宁德时代董事长周一告诉记者，该公司正在讨论在香港设立研发中心，以创造可在海外和行业内获得许可的新技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>华友钴业董事长提出电池材料政策化解产能过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</link><description>据官方媒体周一报道，浙江华友钴业董事长在中国年度人大会议之前提出，中国应采取措施解决锂电池材料行业产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:14:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>克里提升了美国的气候声誉，但世界的信任仍然难以捉摸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</link><description>周三，约翰·克里准备辞去乔·拜登总统气候变化问题特使的职务，这将使美国在全球气候外交中处于更有利的地位，尽管世界舞台上对美国政策意图的不信任挥之不去。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园可能会申请法院命令以验证股份转让</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周一表示，在评估其离岸重组的进展后，将考虑是否有必要在稍后阶段向高等法院申请生效令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>能源部长表示欧盟不能关闭太阳能进口边境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</link><description>欧盟能源政策负责人卡德里·西姆森周一表示，欧盟应该支持陷入困境的欧洲太阳能电池板制造商，但不能对此类产品的进口关闭边境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>解说：本周中国两会的看点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国议会、全国人民代表大会（NPC）将于周二召开年度会议，所有人的目光都集中在支持世界第二大经济体增长的计划上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯表示，如果海洋利益被忽视，菲律宾将反击中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾将在有争议的南海问题上与中国合作，但如果其主权和海洋权利被忽视，菲律宾将予以反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总理组建新联盟，抛弃旧盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</link><description>尼泊尔总理普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔周一任命了三名部长，其中两个反对党各一名，组成新的联盟，抛弃了在其前任政府中占主导地位的中间派尼泊尔国大党。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>BlueBay、格雷厄姆等对冲基金关注日本交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-spot-money-be-made-japan-2024-03-04/</link><description>由于其他主要经济体提高利率以抑制通胀，日本央行长期以来一直处于异类，预计将很快结束其负利率政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-spot-money-be-made-japan-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国自1993年以来首次取消总理年度新闻发布会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</link><description>一名官员周一表示，中国总理李强将不会在今年的年度全国人大会议结束后举行新闻发布会，结束了三十年来的传统。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>